# GradeTrack

## Description
A minimal multi‑course grade‑tracking app that helps students manage assignments and view instant GPA updates.

---

## Features
- Track grades across multiple courses  
- Automatic GPA calculation  
- Assignment and category management  
- Simple, responsive interface  
- Persistent backend storage  

---

## Technologies
- Node.js  
- TypeScript  
- MongoDB 
- HTML / CSS / JavaScript  

---

